<span style="color:#000000;">I am writing this in the slim chance that someone will receive this

I'm casting my warning into the abyss like a message in a bottle amidst an infinite, treacherous ocean.

My name is Julian Harold Charles. And God has cursed me to carry a flame of an impossible task, it feels. 

I have managed to find a computer in the level I'm in. It was somehow completely fine, with no scratches or anything that could have made it unfunctional. There were no logins or anything. It was just there, sitting peacefully. I'm currently typing away in what looks like a bare dairy shop. 

I do not know how much time has passed out there, because time seems to be almost frozen here. The air is cold and stagnant, and I know that I have no hope to get out of here, a deep feeling in the pits of my heart tells me that I'm condemned to walk forever or suffer consequences beyond the sensation of hell.

It is because of this computer that I am even able to document this place. My radio doesn't work, and I couldn't find any other way to send information. If this gets sent, I hope someone will share this information with others so they will not suffer as I do. I am still in here. Please read the file. 

I implore you, with all fiber of whatever being of me remains, do not look for me. 
----
